<br><br>
                    <b>REVERSE RUN EVENT:</b><br>
1st Reverse Run in South India to create awareness on plastic pollution was held in Elliot’s Beach, Besant Nagar, Chennai on 02/07/2022 in which 10 NCC cadets participated. <br>
From our school, 10 NCC cadets participated in 1st Reverse Run for 300m to celebrate Plastic Bag Free Day on 2nd July 2022 Saturday at Elliot's Beach, Besant Nagar. Cadets received Medal, participation certificate and cloth Bag for the Awareness Reverse Run.
